49:23.041 --> 49:23.917
serving two masters,

49:24.000 --> 49:27.709
or should I say,
having the two

49:27.792 --> 49:31.208
actually serve you.

49:33.041 --> 49:36.333
You came up
in Albany politics,

49:36.417 --> 49:38.417
I can't imagine there's
an alignment of forces

49:38.500 --> 49:39.667
you haven't seen before.

49:39.750 --> 49:42.458
Well, I just think
it's fascinating.

49:42.542 --> 49:43.959
Audacious.

49:44.792 --> 49:46.375
That's not always
how it feels.

49:46.458 --> 49:47.625
'Course not.

49:47.709 --> 49:49.417
No, when you're
in it, it's, uh...

49:49.500 --> 49:52.709
well, it's like being
at the bottom of a waterfall.

49:52.792 --> 49:54.083
You can't decide whether
to dive in and swim

49:54.166 --> 49:56.750
or cover your head and try
to get one decent breath

49:56.834 --> 49:59.125
before you expire.

49:59.208 --> 50:01.041
Much like
a campaign,

50:01.125 --> 50:04.333
or being the First Lady
of the state.

50:04.417 --> 50:08.917
It's a shame most folks will
never get to see your act, Jack.

50:09.000 --> 50:11.458
Ah, you and I have
a lot in common that way.

50:12.959 --> 50:13.959
You know, I always found
the most satisfaction--

50:14.041 --> 50:18.250
and the most success--
on the sidelines.

50:18.333 --> 50:20.709
Reading the field,
calling the plays.

50:20.792 --> 50:22.750
Eventually, it, uh...

50:22.834 --> 50:26.000
Well, it was no longer that I
simply had the ears of titans.

50:26.083 --> 50:29.917
I learned to like
moving them around too.

50:30.000 --> 50:34.583
♪ suspenseful music  ♪

50:34.667 --> 50:37.125
What do you do when
there's no play to be made?

50:37.208 --> 50:41.250
When no matter what you choose,
it'll end in disaster?

50:41.333 --> 50:42.166
Classic double-bind.

50:43.333 --> 50:48.291
There's a zen koan where
the teacher holds a stick.

50:48.375 --> 50:52.792
He says to his student, "If you
tell me this stick is real,

50:52.875 --> 50:55.458
I will beat you with it.

50:55.542 --> 50:57.041
If you tell me
it is not real,

50:57.125 --> 50:58.250
I will
beat you with it.

50:58.333 --> 51:03.125
If you say nothing,
I will beat you with it."

51:03.208 --> 51:07.041
And so, the student
reaches out,

51:07.125 --> 51:10.583
grabs the stick,
and breaks it.

51:13.375 --> 51:17.000
If a situation is
untenable, Mrs. Rhoades,

51:17.083 --> 51:19.458
you break
that fucking stick.

51:19.542 --> 51:24.375
♪ suspenseful music  ♪

51:24.458 --> 51:27.166
There is no reason
on this earth

51:27.250 --> 51:31.458
that you should go to jail
while Axelrod doesn't.

51:31.542 --> 51:35.583
If you have taught me anything,
you have taught me that.

51:35.667 --> 51:38.834
I swear, Axelrod is
going down with me.

51:38.917 --> 51:39.792
Do you know how
you're gonna do that?

51:39.875 --> 51:43.500
I had procured
a piece of evidence, a slide,

51:43.583 --> 51:46.000
and I had planned
to use an unsavory character

51:46.083 --> 51:48.166
to plant it
in Axelrod's home;

51:48.250 --> 51:50.417
was prepared to pay dearly
for the operative.

51:50.500 --> 51:53.500
However I now seem
to have run out of options.

51:53.583 --> 51:56.834
Don't tell the kids anything
until the verdict is announced.

51:58.125 --> 52:02.625
And never let them
see your shame.

52:05.208 --> 52:08.500
Bearing, son, is all.

52:13.792 --> 52:15.291
More bad news?

52:15.375 --> 52:17.750
Perhaps the contrary.

52:18.792 --> 52:20.542
I have to go.

52:20.625 --> 52:22.709
Uh...

52:22.792 --> 52:24.667
I've been given
a last chance.

52:25.500 --> 52:28.959
That slide may yet
find purchase.

