53:51.917 --> 53:53.959
Ballsy.

53:54.041 --> 53:56.291
Can we come in?

54:09.875 --> 54:11.250
Huh.

54:11.333 --> 54:13.291
You know, last time I saw you,
you were behind bars.

54:13.375 --> 54:17.667
Tell me, does living
in a space this palatial

54:17.750 --> 54:18.500
actually erase the memory

54:18.583 --> 54:22.709
of that badly lit cell
in Brooklyn?

54:22.792 --> 54:25.750
Or maybe you just felt the need
to swing your dick one last time

54:25.834 --> 54:27.333
in anticipation
of a place far worse.

54:27.417 --> 54:29.166
You managed to get your foot
caught in the rope

54:29.250 --> 54:31.458
tossing me overboard,
there, Chuck.

54:31.542 --> 54:35.000
Now, I may pop to the surface,
but you are going under.

54:35.083 --> 54:35.834
Congratulations.
Enough.

54:35.917 --> 54:37.458
I didn't bring us
all together

54:37.542 --> 54:40.458
