your puerile bullshit.

54:40.542 --> 54:41.625
This is how we ended up here
in the first place.

54:41.709 --> 54:45.333
Because the two of you,
at your absolute fucking worst,

54:45.417 --> 54:48.208
went after each other
like a couple of pit bulls.

54:48.291 --> 54:50.375
And now we're all three of us
royally fucked,

54:50.458 --> 54:53.583
in a way
that's so incestuous

54:53.667 --> 54:56.375
that if one of us
goes to prison, we all do.

54:56.458 --> 54:58.625
Conversely, if we want
to get ourselves

54:58.709 --> 54:59.375
