55:42.083 --> 55:43.917
I'll discuss it.

55:44.000 --> 55:46.250
Why I'm here.

55:46.333 --> 55:46.542
Good.

55:48.959 --> 55:50.500
As much as you two
fucking hate each other,

55:50.583 --> 55:51.500
